name: Samoyed Dogecoin (SAMO)
description: SAMO (Samoyed Dogecoin) is a 100% decentralized community experiment with a total supply of 10 billions. The team transfers 30% of it to Vitalik Buterin's wallet address; Another 30% goes to Facebook founder and CEO Mark Zuckerberg's wallet; The remaining SAMO coins will be used for market circulation, adding value for investors.
